entry.title: SWSSP02
entry.summary:
Vendor: STARMAXDESIGN
Type:
Price: 0.00

Wood silk sound-absorbing panels are made from wood fiber as raw material, combined with a unique adhesive, and under high temperature and high-pressure conditions. Its unique surface silky texture gives people a primitive and rough feeling. The surface of wood wool sound-absorbing panels can be painted and painted, and they are fireproof, high temperature resistant, and impact resistant. Therefore, it is very suitable for use in cinemas, theaters, concert halls, hotels, conference rooms, libraries, research rooms, gyms, sports venues, churches, schools, kindergartens, bowling halls, and other places where sound absorption and noise processing are required.
